Introduced Version
HOUSE BILL No. 1322
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 25-34.1-3-4.1.
Synopsis: Attorney eligibility for real estate broker exam. Allows a
licensed attorney to obtain a real estate broker license without
completing an approved broker course of study.
Effective: Upon passage; July 1, 2026.
Hatcher
January 6, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Employment, Labor and
Pensions.
2026 IN 1322—LS 6293/DI 153

Introduced
Second Regular Session of the 124th General Assembly (2026)
PRINTING CODE. Amendments: Whenever an existing statute (or a section of the Indiana
